    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and bodywork. The engine currently runs roughly and has several fluid leaks, while the exterior shows major dents, significant paint peeling, and visible rust. The interior exhibits heavy wear, including torn upholstery and several non-functional electronic components. This car is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts, and we strongly recommend a full inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
